{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 254, "title": "Cache expensive resources in privacy plugin", "body": "Refactored privacy_plugin to use singleton instances for AnalyzerEngine and AnonymizerEngine, preventing repeated initialization and improving performance. Added tests to verify resource caching, singleton reuse, and performance across multiple invocations.\r\n\r\nFixes #253 ", "baseRefName": "main", "baseRefOid": "6d097211ed061a9d2b61a0625905deffde907719", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "algorithmicsuperintelligence/optillm"}, "url": "https://github.com/algorithmicsuperintelligence/optillm/pull/254", "createdAt": "2025-09-29T01:20:34Z", "mergedAt": "2025-09-29T01:40:49Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "algorithmicsuperintelligence/optillm"}, "sha": "6d097211ed061a9d2b61a0625905deffde907719"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/algorithmicsuperintelligence/optillm/pull/254.diff", "number": 254, "created_at": "2025-09-29T01:20:34Z", "merged_at": "2025-09-29T01:40:49Z", "resolved_issues": [253]}
{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 258, "title": "Add configurable SSL certificate verification support", "body": "Introduces SSL verification and custom CA bundle configuration via CLI and environment variables. Updates server, plugins, and clients to propagate SSL settings, adds documentation (README.md, SSL_CONFIGURATION.md), and provides a test suite for SSL configuration. Security warnings are logged when SSL verification is disabled.\r\n\r\n- fixes #256 ", "baseRefName": "main", "baseRefOid": "6956fd1eb1d157dcb13ce2d27dfc2daeeeae6369", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "algorithmicsuperintelligence/optillm"}, "url": "https://github.com/algorithmicsuperintelligence/optillm/pull/258", "createdAt": "2025-09-30T04:16:49Z", "mergedAt": "2025-09-30T05:17:10Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "algorithmicsuperintelligence/optillm"}, "sha": "6956fd1eb1d157dcb13ce2d27dfc2daeeeae6369"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/algorithmicsuperintelligence/optillm/pull/258.diff", "number": 258, "created_at": "2025-09-30T04:16:49Z", "merged_at": "2025-09-30T05:17:10Z", "resolved_issues": [256]}
{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 261, "title": "Refactor TTD-DR plugin for improved citation handling", "body": "Updated the README to clarify the TTD-DR algorithm steps, highlight implemented and future features, and update the architecture diagram. In research_engine.py, removed the unused memory-based synthesis, added citation usage validation, improved citation requirements in denoising and finalization steps, and ensured only used citations are included in the final references. Enhanced metadata and documentation for future self-evolutionary optimization.\r\n\r\nFixes #260 ", "baseRefName": "main", "baseRefOid": "82b6c2411d1d5bf8a67d11be36c32b251f91a947", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "algorithmicsuperintelligence/optillm"}, "url": "https://github.com/algorithmicsuperintelligence/optillm/pull/261", "createdAt": "2025-10-15T23:09:29Z", "mergedAt": "2025-10-15T23:29:10Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "algorithmicsuperintelligence/optillm"}, "sha": "82b6c2411d1d5bf8a67d11be36c32b251f91a947"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/algorithmicsuperintelligence/optillm/pull/261.diff", "number": 261, "created_at": "2025-10-15T23:09:29Z", "merged_at": "2025-10-15T23:29:10Z", "resolved_issues": [260]}
{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 266, "title": "Add robust response validation and token config support", "body": "Introduces consistent None and truncation checks for model responses across all major modules, improving error handling and fallback behavior. Adds support for max_completion_tokens in request configuration, with priority over max_tokens, and propagates this through plugin and server layers. Enhances logging for truncated or empty responses and ensures backward compatibility for token limit parameters.\r\n\r\nfixes #262 and fixes #264 ", "baseRefName": "main", "baseRefOid": "427b8fe5ecbd8994aaa5c9df0e0a07117b7d13fd", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "algorithmicsuperintelligence/optillm"}, "url": "https://github.com/algorithmicsuperintelligence/optillm/pull/266", "createdAt": "2025-11-01T07:13:00Z", "mergedAt": "2025-11-01T08:27:05Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "algorithmicsuperintelligence/optillm"}, "sha": "427b8fe5ecbd8994aaa5c9df0e0a07117b7d13fd"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/algorithmicsuperintelligence/optillm/pull/266.diff", "number": 266, "created_at": "2025-11-01T07:13:00Z", "merged_at": "2025-11-01T08:27:05Z", "resolved_issues": [262, 264]}
